##THIS NEEDS TO BE ADDED AS A FEATURE.
IMPLEMENT WITH BLOOD HUNTERS

Lesser Pacts

Sometimes to destroy one evil, we must ally ourselves with another. Such is the way of Blood Hunters that have taken to the Order of the Profane Soul. Should a Blood Hunter walk this path, they may chose to form a pact with the Puppeteer. If they do, they gain the following.

Rite Focus
The Puppeteer. If you use the Blood Curse of the Fallen Puppet, you can use that blood curse again on the same creature as a bonus action on your next turn without expending a use of your Blood Maledict.

Revealed Arcana
The Puppeteer. You can cast ventriloquism once using a pact spell slot. You can't do so again until you finish a long rest.

Unsealed Arcana
The Puppeteer. You can cast animate dead once using a pact spell slot. You can't do so again until you finish a long rest.

